{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Judenrate got-- you know, came to the houses and said, you, you, you, and you, you have to go to work, or you have to come and help or whatever.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how they were getting us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, the names were enough for them to know we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And besides, I guess we had the-- all the Jews had to register.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, even-- even during the Russian times, when we were with the Russians, we were given like a-- it's not a passport, but it was like a document that looked almost like a passport.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they ask what-- what was-- where you were born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you were born in the western part of Poland, you were called this-- you were under certain paragraph.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they knew if they wanted to-- the Russians-- if they wanted to send you-- to send all the refugees to-- to Russia, they would-- they-- it was just enough to look at that paragraph.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was the religion stated in the-- in those [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think that we had to register when the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we had to register.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the Jews probably had to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they created that Judenrate, probably all the Jews had to go and register.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the house we were living in became part of a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was probably not too long after the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, I remember we had a two-- one bedroom and a living room, yes, and a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were four people-- the four and my two uncles were with us at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we're six people.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
